[normal]Since the Rugby Football Union for Women was integrated with the RFU, the RFU does not separate its sponsorship of women’s and men’s programmes.    The
[normal] RFU has a strong commercial 
[normal]programme
[normal], and works with partners to ensure that they have a far-reaching and embedded place within England rugby.
[normal]  This ensures the m
[normal]aximum commercial investment in
[normal]to all aspects of the Game, including women’s rugby.
