[normal]The RFU
[normal] as an employer is committed to
[normal] achieving the National Equality Standard devised by Ernst and Young 
[normal]by 2015.  
[normal]The current gender ratio of 
[normal]employee
[normal]s is approximately 70% male and 30% 
[normal]female,
[normal] with initial investigative re
[normal]search indicating that average salaries by grade and gender does not give rise to equality issues.
